[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "マリオン",
		"romanized_name": "Marion",
		"model_path_hash": "2676271994623593349",
		"text": "「飴」の所持者の位置を把握できる装置、\nついに完成よ！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5397390121100149522",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "マリオン",
		"romanized_name": "Marion",
		"model_path_hash": "2676271994623593349",
		"text": "そしてなんと……支援物資を届ける機能も\nついでに作ることができたわ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5397390121100149522",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "リリー",
		"romanized_name": "Lilie",
		"model_path_hash": "3156259592327480116",
		"text": "これで、遠く離れた仲間にも必要なものを\nすぐに届けられますね。旅がずっと安心になります",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1808607659247495452",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "プラフタ",
		"romanized_name": "Plachta",
		"model_path_hash": "894414068988709786",
		"text": "スールたちが作っていた「イタズラ装置」を\n応用したのが功を奏しました",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8944192761651257696",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "プラフタ",
		"romanized_name": "Plachta",
		"model_path_hash": "894414068988709786",
		"text": "亜空の道を通じて、\n「飴」を持つ者の元へ物資を転送できます",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8944192761651257696",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "プラフタ",
		"romanized_name": "Plachta",
		"model_path_hash": "894414068988709786",
		"text": "ただ、送ることができるのはあくまで「物」のみで、\n亜空の道を利用した人の移動は実現できませんでした",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8944192761651257696",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ロジー",
		"romanized_name": "Logy",
		"model_path_hash": "3061836162665800468",
		"text": "それだけ、ハルフェンに居たというクルシュアは\n特別な力を持っていたということだな",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8747806484636614570",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ロジー",
		"romanized_name": "Logy",
		"model_path_hash": "3061836162665800468",
		"text": "しかし、まさかイタズラが役に立つとはな……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8747806484636614570",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "……奇跡みたいな偶然ね。\nまあ、実用性は高いし、悪くない",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "マリオン",
		"romanized_name": "Marion",
		"model_path_hash": "2676271994623593349",
		"text": "ただし！　絶対にイタズラには使わないこと！\n分かったわね、スール！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5397390121100149522",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "スール",
		"romanized_name": "Suelle",
		"model_path_hash": "3072540865312949120",
		"text": "ご、ごめんなさい……\nもうイタズラには使いません……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8906082768242880907",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ユーディー",
		"romanized_name": "Judie",
		"model_path_hash": "2697025160672431728",
		"text": "ほんとに反省してるから、許して……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2032894617718182411",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "マリオン",
		"romanized_name": "Marion",
		"model_path_hash": "2676271994623593349",
		"text": "まったく……今度やったら、アトリエ出禁よ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5397390121100149522",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "レント",
		"romanized_name": "Lent",
		"model_path_hash": "2885764269898401541",
		"text": "なんか、便利なものができたらしいな",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2104807859548338143",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ルーウェン",
		"romanized_name": "Ruven",
		"model_path_hash": "5045126258635234854",
		"text": "……なあ、レント。どうせなら、アトリエから\n強力な攻撃も届けられたらいいのにって思わないか？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8255125025153112443",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "レント",
		"romanized_name": "Lent",
		"model_path_hash": "2885764269898401541",
		"text": "確かにな。デッカイ大砲作ってさ、\nどこにいてもドカーンと一発撃てたら最高だよな",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2104807859548338143",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ルーウェン",
		"romanized_name": "Ruven",
		"model_path_hash": "5045126258635234854",
		"text": "砲弾はマリーに頼めば、\nきっととんでもないのを作ってくれるぜ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8255125025153112443",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "マリー",
		"romanized_name": "Marie",
		"model_path_hash": "1543991191416950894",
		"text": "あんたたち、物騒なこと考えてるわね……\nそんな大砲ができるなら、もちろん協力するけど",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1729358731240541415",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "レント",
		"romanized_name": "Lent",
		"model_path_hash": "2885764269898401541",
		"text": "やっぱ無理かあ？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2104807859548338143",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ルーウェン",
		"romanized_name": "Ruven",
		"model_path_hash": "5045126258635234854",
		"text": "いいや！　夢は終わらねえ。\nいつか必ず実現してやるさ！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8255125025153112443",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "レント",
		"romanized_name": "Lent",
		"model_path_hash": "2885764269898401541",
		"text": "そうだな……男の浪漫ってやつだ！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2104807859548338143",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "マリー",
		"romanized_name": "Marie",
		"model_path_hash": "1543991191416950894",
		"text": "なんか燃えてる……そのうちアトリエに\n巨大な大砲が建ってたりして",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1729358731240541415",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "マリー",
		"romanized_name": "Marie",
		"model_path_hash": "1543991191416950894",
		"text": "……まさかね？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1729358731240541415",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]